snippet.title: BIOTA Swarm - Official Gameplay Overview Trailer
snippet.description: BIOTA Swarm is a bullet hell roguelite shooter inspired by games like Vampire Survivors. The latest trailer runs through its characters, weapon upgrades, and how the randomly generated levels will offer unique challenges with each playthrough.
